in risk management at the consultancy Accenture. "Business, and not just the=
=20
energy business, just has to be part of it on every level, or it risks=20
getting burned."=20
NEW TOOLS=20
Besides the internationally tradeable carbon pollution credits, the=20
governments agreed initiatives such as Clean Development Mechanisms (CDMs)=20
that allow developed nations to score credits by funding climate friendly=20
